      <title>woah my first sold out arena show at msg! thank you so much to all the twiglets ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWSD4ZcibBr/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656427703_18580728463055762_2380240611975239823_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=1&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDE2Mzc0NDA1OTk1MzA1MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOS5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=MNVFD1s_J88Q7kNvwFLqZ_T&amp;_nc_oc=AdquNd5CAFZrGPqGuVHRUJaF-shOR7g1nzQ1792l_FhdgSyZPV7Rz6A79YwOU6f6jV4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9GMw0YofY4A9h3kVYccZjQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzKy4BZll3befhSkxpBLSBp9el7TzNPr1lnIivjoIxv3A&amp;oe=69C8DF59" alt="Instagram billede fra @fkatwigs" /></p><p><strong>@fkatwigs</strong></p><p>woah my first sold out arena show at msg! thank you so much to all the twiglets who have believed in me and supported me for the past 15 years!<br/>
through all the genres i have explored and body movements i have learnt you have always been there to support me and allowed me to grow in all directions, perfectly twisted and nurtured, i am your bonsai tree. you are my super heroes and we are creating a magical sci-fi together. thank you thank you thank you to all of my creative family who helped create this moment with me, more posts to come expressing my gratitude to you xxx</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656427703_18580728463055762_2380240611975239823_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=1&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDE2Mzc0NDA1OTk1MzA1MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOS5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=MNVFD1s_J88Q7kNvwFLqZ_T&amp;_nc_oc=AdquNd5CAFZrGPqGuVHRUJaF-shOR7g1nzQ1792l_FhdgSyZPV7Rz6A79YwOU6f6jV4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9GMw0YofY4A9h3kVYccZjQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzKy4BZll3befhSkxpBLSBp9el7TzNPr1lnIivjoIxv3A&amp;oe=69C8DF59" alt="Instagram billede fra @fkatwigs" /></p><p><strong>@fkatwigs</strong></p><p>woah my first sold out arena show at msg! thank you so much to all the twiglets who have believed in me and supported me for the past 15 years!<br/>
through all the genres i have explored and body movements i have learnt you have always been there to support me and allowed me to grow in all directions, perfectly twisted and nurtured, i am your bonsai tree. you are my super heroes and we are creating a magical sci-fi together. thank you thank you thank you to all of my creative family who helped create this moment with me, more posts to come expressing my gratitude to you xxx</p>]]></content:encoded>
